node.text: It all started as a dream and our team of engineers made it a reality. Learn how testing at Nürburgring to implement new architecture and technology took the mid-engine #Corvette to the next level. #Stingray #Vette #C8

node.title: Revolution: The Mid-Engine Corvette Development Story – Part 2: Engineering

node.text: The revolutionary design of the mid-engine #Corvette was inspired by aircraft and racecars. Learn more unexpected facts and see how the design has paved the way for generations to come. #Stingray #Vette #C8
